We &apos;re at a unique moment in history , says UK Prime Minister Gordon Brown : we can use today &apos;s interconnectedness to develop our shared global ethic -- and work together to confront the challenges of poverty , security , climate change and the economy .
Can I say how delighted I am to be away from the calm of Westminster and Whitehall ?
This is Kim , a nine-year-old Vietnam girl , her back ruined by napalm , and she awakened the conscience of the nation of America to begin to end the Vietnam War .
