Here &apos;s a crazy idea : Persuade the world to try living in peace for just one day , every September 21 . In this energetic , honest talk , Jeremy Gilley tells the story of how this crazy idea became real -- real enough to help millions of kids in war-torn regions .
I was basically concerned about what was going on in the world .
